{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for the most chaotic, gas-fueled adventure of your life! In <strong>Bean House: Escape The Hitler</strong>, you must collect all the beans to unleash the ultimate power\u2014farts strong enough to free innocent meme characters from their prison.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But beware! The sinister <strong>Hitler</strong>, the terrifying <strong>Killer Tomato</strong>, and the unstoppable <strong>John Xina</strong> stand in your way. These relentless guardians will do whatever it takes to stop you from reaching the beans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3525800/extras/JohnTxtt.gif?t=1740417586\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge, strategize, and outmaneuver them while harnessing the power of your bean-fueled flatulence. Can you outsmart the guards, collect every last bean, and break your friends free?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3525800/extras/floww.gif?t=1740417586\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong><br>\ud83d\udd25 <strong>Hilarious, meme-fueled chaos</strong><br>\ud83e\uded8 <strong>Bean-collecting, fart-powered gameplay</strong><br>\ud83d\udea8 <strong>Stealth and strategy\u2014avoid deadly guards!</strong><br>\ud83d\ude02 <strong>Absurd, unpredictable encounters</strong><br>\ud83c\udfae <strong>Release all the innocent memes prisoners and win the game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Bean House awaits\u2026 will you rise to the challenge, or will you be stopped by the guards? Play now and unleash the power of the beans!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3525800/extras/cat.gif?t=1740417586\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.stea